list.name: Default
list.comment: Added support for starting with a pre-populated database.

task.summary: First save point on view flipper
Removed cloning library as I wasn't able to get it working correctly.
First iteration (not fully working yet) of the recipe flipper. Also implemented the Action Bar Sherlock library (no tabs or anything set up yet).
Finished next iteration of navigation. Nav buttons now send you to correct activity and I was able to extract all the nav data into a common MyCheeseActivity class.
Now reselecting the same tab will bring you back to that tab's activity if you aren't on that activity anymore.
Added JournalHome which will list all of the current journals. Also supports deleting those journals but not yet the detailed page for the journal yet.

Fixed tab target when changing to a journalInfo activity. Now stays on Journal tab.
Also fixed navigation capitalization bug

Implemented standalone Journal home and info activities.
Also fixed navigation capitalization bug
Curling effect for recipes is now starting to be in a working state (still much more tuning left)
Portrait view mode curl effect now in working state
Update portrait view mode further tuning. Now passing correct width and size for bitmap creation
Added dynamic alarm that can detect times within the current recipe page and then pop up a timer count down for the time.
Let's get the countdown timer library in git.

MESSAGE.value: First save point on view flipper
Added Glossary activity.
Removed cloning library as I wasn't able to get it working correctly.
First iteration (not fully working yet) of the recipe flipper. Also implemented the Action Bar Sherlock library (no tabs or anything set up yet).
Finished next iteration of navigation. Nav buttons now send you to correct activity and I was able to extract all the nav data into a common MyCheeseActivity class.
Now reselecting the same tab will bring you back to that tab's activity if you aren't on that activity anymore.
Added JournalHome which will list all of the current journals. Also supports deleting those journals but not yet the detailed page for the journal yet.

Fixed tab target when changing to a journalInfo activity. Now stays on Journal tab.
Also fixed navigation capitalization bug

Implemented standalone Journal home and info activities.
Also fixed navigation capitalization bug
Curling effect for recipes is now starting to be in a working state (still much more tuning left)
Portrait view mode curl effect now in working state
Update portrait view mode further tuning. Now passing correct width and size for bitmap creation
Curl effect now works with recipes from db
Curl effect now works with recipes from db. Also separated out the recipe start layout from the recipe activity into its own RecipeStart activity.
Set up home button in nav bar
Navigation tabs now only appear on the Home, Cheeses, Journal and Glossary activities
Recipe text now doesn't break in the middle of words between pages.
Journal is now editable. I also put in place the ability to scroll automatically to the last journal entry they were editing. Unfortunately it's not an exact science, but it serves it's purpose.
Fixed date time storage/appearance for journal entries.
Useless imports begone!

You can now create a new journal, or go to a previous journal directly from a recipe. Once you have selected a journal it saves it in memory and subsequent clicks to edit journal will take you right to it.
Added a bunch of icons from an icon pack I believe I'll use.
Added dynamic alarm that can detect times within the current recipe page and then pop up a timer count down for the time.
Let's get the countdown timer library in git.
